/* fonts */
export const FontFamily = {
  robotoBold: "Roboto-Bold",
  robotoMedium: "Roboto-Medium",
  robotoSerifSemiBold: "RobotoSerif-SemiBold",
  noah: "Noah",
  bodyLargeBold: "Urbanist-Bold",
  sFProText: "SF Pro Text",
  robotoRegular: "Roboto-Regular",
  robotoThin: "Roboto-Thin",
  robotoBlack: "Roboto-Black",
  robotoLight: "Roboto-Light",
};
/* font sizes */
export const FontSize = {
  size_xs: 12,
  size_sm: 14,
  size_21xl: 40,
  size_mini: 15,
  bodyLargeBold_size: 16,
  size_65xl: 84,
  size_13xl: 32,
  size_sm_3: 13,
  size_3xl_7: 23,
};
/* Colors */
export const Color = {
  othersWhite: "#fff",
  colorDarkslategray: "#373a44",
  colorRoyalblue: "#246bfd",
  colorGray_100: "#75777d",
  lighterDark: "#23262f",
  greyscale900: "#212121",
  colorGray_200: "#181a20",
  colorGray_300: "rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6)",
  colorGray_400: "rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.24)",
  colorGray_500: "rgba(21, 21, 21, 0.64)",
  colorWhitesmoke: "#eee",
  colorBlack: "#056",
  colorSlategray: "#70768a",
  colorOrange: "#ffb920",
  colorDimgray: "#6b6d71",
  colorDarkgray: "#9598a1",
};
/* Paddings */
export const Padding = {
  p_base: 16,
  p_31xl: 50,
  p_19xl: 38,
  p_13xl: 32,
};
/* border radiuses */
export const Border = {
  br_11xs: 2,
  br_5xl: 24,
  br_12xl: 31,
  br_11xs_3: 1,
  br_10xs_7: 3,
  br_5xs: 8,
  br_81xl: 100,
  br_23xl: 42,
  br_13xl: 32,
  br_7xs: 6,
  br_5xs_9: 8,
  br_5xs_6: 8,
  br_9xs: 4,
  br_xs: 12,
};
